article.description: — Ajay Mitchell had a season-high 31 points as UC Santa Barbara beat UC Davis 76-69 in overtime on Thursday night.
article.headline: Mitchell leads UC Santa Barbara over UC Davis 76-69 in OT
article.linkText: Mitchell leads UC Santa Barbara over UC Davis 76-69 in OT
article.story: DAVIS, Calif. -- — Ajay Mitchell had a season-high 31 points as UC Santa Barbara beat UC Davis 76-69 in overtime on Thursday night. The Gauchos ended the game with a 10-2 run. Amadou Sow had 17 points and 11 rebounds for UC Santa Barbara (13-10, 6-6 Big West Conference). Josh Pierre-Louis added 14 points. Miles Norris had eight rebounds. Elijah Pepper had 21 points for the Aggies (11-8, 5-4). Ezra Manjon added 19 points and six assists. Kane Milling had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
